## Configuration File

Create a `{{name}}.config.js` file in your project root:

```javascript
export default {
  // Your configuration here
};
```

## TypeScript Support

For TypeScript projects, use `{{name}}.config.ts`:

```typescript
import type { Config } from '{{name}}';

const config: Config = {
  // Type-safe configuration
};

export default config;
```
